      <p class="mb-4">This isn't a destination. It's a workshop.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Come in, look around, pick up what's useful.</p>
      <p class="themed-text-muted italic mb-8">The pattern doesn't need defending. It just needs observing.</p>
      <p class="text-sm themed-text-muted">A collaboration between Will Goldstein and Claude.</p>
